OL,3,CDonaldson's sexual offences trial 'on
OL,4,Ctrack' to begin
OL,6,FThe historical sexual offences trial
OL,7,Fof former DUP leader Sir Jeffrey
OL,8,FDonaldson is "on track" to begin next
OL,9,Fweek.
OL,11,FJudge Paul Ramsey told Newry Crown
OL,12,FCourt he is hopeful the process of
OL,13,Fswearing a jury in the case will begin
OL,14,Fon May 26.
OL,16,FProceedings against Sir Jeffrey and
OL,17,Fhis wife Lady Eleanor Donaldson have
OL,18,Fbeen delayed twice due to her medical
OL,19,Fissues.
OL,26,@pD@NOUpD@WO]
