OL,3,CDonaldson's sexual offences trial 'on
OL,4,Ctrack' to begin
OL,6,FJeffrey Donaldson, 63, has pleaded not
OL,7,Fguilty to 18 alleged offences.
OL,9,FThe charges include one count of rape
OL,10,Fand allegations of indecent assault
OL,11,Fand gross indecency, and span a time
OL,12,Fperiod between 1985 and 2008,
OL,13,Finvolving two alleged victims.
OL,15,FEleanor Donaldson, 60, from Dromore,
OL,16,Fis facing charges of aiding and
OL,17,Fabetting, which she denies.
OL,19,FNeither of the Donaldsons attended
OL,20,FTuesday's hearing in Newry courthouse.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/4
