OL,3,CDonaldson's sexual offences trial 'on
OL,4,Ctrack' to begin
OL,6,FDuring the brief hearing, the judge
OL,7,Fsaid the court had received a report
OL,8,Frelating to Eleanor Donaldson which
OL,9,Fwould require some legal argument.
OL,11,FThe judge said: "We are on track to
OL,12,Fcommence the case next Tuesday."
OL,14,FProsecuting barrister Rosemary Walsh
OL,15,FKC said the timeline worked "as far as
OL,16,Fthe prosecution is concerned".
OL,18,FDefence barristers also indicated they
OL,19,Fhoped to be in a position to begin the
OL,20,Fcase next week.
